    "type": "Artifice",
    "subType": "Assist",
    "description": "An artifice item that replaces a lost limb or body part. Each of these must be custom made for a person. When attached, it allows the user to function as if the artifice limb was a normal limb. Mods A mods: Grapple Launcher (Arm only)(10 points): Allows the user to install a grappling hook artifice in the arm, functioning just like the grappling hook would. (Grappling hook must be supplied separately and takes an errand action from an artificer to install). A grappling hook installed in the arm takes burden like usual and still takes an AP to activate, but requires no AP to pull out. Zoom In (Eye only)(20 points): You may spend 1 AP to gain a +10 bonus to your perception until the start of your next turn. Weapon Slot (Arm only)(20 points): Allows the user to install a weapon into the arm, functioning just like the weapon would (takes an errand from artificer to install). The weapon costs burden like normal, but may be drawn or sheathed for 0 AP once per turn. Movement Burst (Leg only) (20 points): You may spend 0 AP to gain +20ft movement until the start of your next turn. Afterwards, your movement speed is halved until you put in a new shell into your leg. B mods: Blast Knuckle (Arm or Leg only) (25 points): After making a Heavy unarmed attack with the limb, you may spend 0 RP to make a Light attack against all enemies in a 15ft wide, 15ft long cone behind the target. After doing this, you must put in a new shell into the limb to use it again (your movement speed is halved if your leg is unusable). Rocket Punch (Arm only) (50 points): Once per round, you may make a basic unarmed Heavy attack with this limb to a target within 60ft. Thermal Fusion Sight (Eye only)(80 points): Adds thermal vision up to 120ft. This cannot detect things hidden by magical means.  The sight can not discern a difference in heat once something reaches freezing temperatures.",
