    "type": "Equipment",
    "subType": "Weapon",
    "description": "Dueling: When attacking a single enemy during a turn at least 3 times with this weapon, your next Dodge or Block against that enemy costs 0 RP until the start of your next turn. This property cannot be used if you target any other enemy during your turn or if you spend AP making a Heavy attack against the target. Mods A mods: Spade Lunga (10 points): When moving at least 40ft towards an enemy, increases the range of your next attack made with this weapon by 5 ft. Ornate Blade (35 points): Moving into the target's threatened zone the first time in a turn counts as 1 attack for the requirement to activate Dueling. B mods: Paired Duelers (25 points): When wielding two dueling weapons with paired duelers, your offhand extra attack counts as one attack for your dueling bonus on your main hand weapon. Passato Sotto (80 points): You may make 1 Heavy attack with this weapon and still gain the dueling effect. Ferrobri Grip (80 points):  Dueling weapon passive changes to Aggressive Dueling: When attacking a single enemy 3 times with this weapon in 1 turn, your next basic attack with this weapon this turn has its cost reduced by 1 AP. Once per round.",
